She's okay. She's okay.

362
00:27:04.247 --> 00:27:06.583
But I think she overdosed.

363
00:27:09.044 --> 00:27:10.253
Oh...

364
00:27:11.671 --> 00:27:13.673
Come here. Come here.

365
00:27:17.177 --> 00:27:19.387
It's my fault.

366
00:27:22.140 --> 00:27:24.392
She hated
herself for being so weak

367
00:27:24.476 --> 00:27:26.686
and passive and afraid.

368
00:27:26.770 --> 00:27:29.356
So. a couple of days
after Cal came over.

369
00:27:29.439 --> 00:27:31.441
she decided to say something.

370
00:27:35.904 --> 00:27:38.865
♪ Yeah. do you think it's
cute that I'm so fucking stupid ♪

371
00:27:38.948 --> 00:27:40.241
♪ Tired of bein' useless ♪

372
00:27:40.325 --> 00:27:41.565
♪ I've been up for three days ♪

373
00:27:41.618 --> 00:27:44.037
♪ Everything is haunted.
everybody's evil ♪

374
00:27:44.120 --> 00:27:46.373
♪ And there's bugs
inside the carpet ♪

375
00:27:46.456 --> 00:27:47.791
