380
00:27:54.923 --> 00:27:57.967
♪ Little blurry stars
scattered all across my room ♪

381
00:28:07.018 --> 00:28:08.770
Now. I didn't know any of this

382
00:28:08.853 --> 00:28:12.023
'cause I was with Elliot
smokin' a little bit of weed.

383
00:28:12.107 --> 00:28:14.359
Jules invited me over
to her house for dinner.

384
00:28:14.442 --> 00:28:18.071
I guess like to apologize.
but I had NA that night

385
00:28:18.154 --> 00:28:20.156
so I went to Elliot's for a bit.

386
00:28:20.240 --> 00:28:23.243
♪ Long as I've got your love ♪

387
00:28:23.326 --> 00:28:26.079
♪ You know that
