389
00:28:30.333 --> 00:28:33.628
♪ I had no doubt in my mind ♪

390
00:28:33.711 --> 00:28:38.049
♪ And it's been you. woman ♪

391
00:28:38.133 --> 00:28:41.469
♪ Right down the line ♪

392
00:28:44.472 --> 00:28:49.060
♪ I just wanna say
this is my way ♪

393
00:28:49.144 --> 00:28:52.605
