415
00:30:12.894 --> 00:30:14.187
Loss.

416
00:30:15.605 --> 00:30:17.106
You think?

417
00:30:18.274 --> 00:30:19.609
Yeah. I think so.

418
00:30:22.487 --> 00:30:24.697
Yeah.

419
00:30:24.781 --> 00:30:26.581
I don't know. Maybe
that's what it was. right?

420
00:30:26.658 --> 00:30:28.409
Like...

421
