Ugh. 'cause I'm good at my job.

454
00:32:02.587 --> 00:32:05.173
Do you think it's a good
thing that we're friends?

455
00:32:06.424 --> 00:32:07.759
Yeah. why?

456
00:32:08.968 --> 00:32:10.762
I just feel like...

457
00:32:10.845 --> 00:32:14.140
we might not bring out
the best in each other.

458
00:32:17.101 --> 00:32:19.145
I feel like I'm okay with that.

459
00:32:24.817 --> 00:32:26.194
I love you.

460
00:32:26.277 --> 00:32:28.905
- I love you.
- I love you more.

461
00:32:28.988 --> 00:32:30.573
I love you more than more.

462
00:32:32.367 --> 00:32:35.745
My god. no.

463
00:32:37.747 --> 00:32:41.000
Ethan made plans with
Kat to go bowling that night.

464
00:32:41.084 --> 00:32:43.252
Kat was depressed because
she couldn't figure out why

465
00:32:43.336 --> 00:32:45.380
she didn't love Ethan.

466
00:32:45.463 --> 00:32:49.217
So she decided to make
a list of pros and cons.

467
00:33:08.653 --> 00:33:10.488
But she couldn't
think of anything.

468
00:33:10.571 --> 00:33:13.408
which made her realize
Ethan might not be the problem.

469
00:33:13.491 --> 00:33:15.660
Mmm.

470
00:33:19.038 --> 00:33:21.416
Rue Kat hated herself.

471
00:33:21.499 --> 00:33:24.711
But the problem with hating
yourself is you can't really talk about it.

472
00:33:24.794 --> 00:33:26.421
Because at some point recently.

473
00:33:26.504 --> 00:33:28.172
the whole world
joined a self-help cult

474
00:33:28.256 --> 00:33:29.799
