the fuck up about it.

475
00:33:29.882 --> 00:33:32.260
It's not gonna solve
all your life problems.

476
00:33:32.343 --> 00:33:33.845
but it is gonna solve...

477
00:33:33.928 --> 00:33:35.638
Kat.

478
00:33:35.722 --> 00:33:36.931
You're one of the bravest.

479
00:33:37.014 --> 00:33:38.683
most beautiful human beings

480
00:33:38.766 --> 00:33:40.435
I have ever seen.

481
00:33:40.518 --> 00:33:43.980
- That's not true.
- Yes. it is.

482
00:33:44.063 --> 00:33:46.357
I wish I had your confidence.

483
00:33:46.441 --> 00:33:49.402
But I don't. like...
feel healthy.

484
00:33:49.485 --> 00:33:50.903
Yes. you are.

485
00:33:50.987 --> 00:33:54.532
No. like... seriously. I'm not.

486
00:33:54.615 --> 00:33:57.160
Kat. you just have
to love yourself.

487
00:33:57.243 --> 00:33:59.036
But that's what
I'm trying to tell you!

488
00:33:59.120 --> 00:34:01.414
I fucking hate myself!

489
00:34:01.497 --> 00:34:04.459
Every day you get out of bed...

490
00:34:04.542 --> 00:34:06.043
It's an act of courage.

491
00:34:06.127 --> 00:34:07.211
That's easy for you to say.

492
00:34:07.295 --> 00:34:09.255
You don't have like
fucking mental problems.

493
00:34:09.338 --> 00:34:12.717
Yes. I do. Why do you
think I look like this?

494
00:34:12.800 --> 00:34:14.135
Are you kidding?

495
00:34:14.217 --> 00:34:16.471
I wish my mental problems
made me look like you.

496
00:34:16.554 --> 00:34:18.556
- Trust me. you don't.
- Trust me. I do!

497
00:34:18.639 --> 00:34:21.034
You're like the most beautiful
person I've ever fucking seen.

498
00:34:21.058 --> 00:34:24.395
Maybe by a white. cis-male.
heteronormative standard.

499
00:34:24.478 --> 00:34:26.938
Oh my god. Are
you fucking joking?!

500
00:34:27.023 --> 00:34:28.775
Kat! Are you
fucking serious?!

501
00:34:28.858 --> 00:34:31.152
That's not you fucking
talking! It's the patriarchy!

502
00:34:31.235 --> 00:34:34.112
It is me talking!
You are not listening!

503
00:34:34.197 --> 00:34:36.282
No! Society puts
things into your mind!

504
00:34:36.364 --> 00:34:39.952
I don't care about
society! I feel like shit!

505
00:34:40.036 --> 00:34:43.080
Kat. you need to smash
all beauty standards.

506
00:34:43.164 --> 00:34:44.998
But I can't even get out of bed!

507
00:34:45.081 --> 00:34:46.458
You have to love yourself.

508
00:34:46.542 --> 00:34:48.262
You need to find your
inner fuckin' warrior!

509
00:34:48.293 --> 00:34:51.130
- Become a bad bitch.
